						               													<description>A game about cooperation, bluffing and deception.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Sabot&amp;oslash;r (&amp;quot;Saboteur&amp;quot;) is a game where good cooperation is the key to success! Together with your teammates, you must cross the Atlantic Ocean in a galleon, but there are secret saboteurs who have only one goal in mind: Make sure the ship never reaches its destination, without being revealed.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This is a game where it can be fatal to trust other players. A game where your best friends will never hesitate to throw you into the sea and where you still depend on working together to reach the goal.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;One person is Captain, changing each turn, and everyone gets 2 action cards they can play any time. Each round good and bad cards are passed around, everyone removing 1 card secretly and the Captain reveals the 3 remaining cards. He rolls a dice and the ship only moves forward if the roll is higher than red cards. Provision is automatically depleted by 1 each round. Everyone can get more action cards, shooting eachother, making someone walk the plank, get fish for extra food and so on. Hopefully the ship reach the destination, so the Saboteurs doesn't win!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
